---
title: "Credit - Powershop, a better power company"
section: "residential"
promotionID: "1245"
promotionName: "$150 Credit & SG Offer (1245)"
customClass: "new-150credit"
openTermsAndConditionsInNewPage: "yes"
---

<section class="header-background magenta white-type text-center">
  <h2>You really can't lose with powershop</h2>
</section>

<section class="light-grey mobile-white promo-body">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered medium-11 columns end">
      <div class="row padding white">
        <div class="small-12 small-centered medium-11 columns end">
          <h2 class="pink-type titles">Sign up to a better power company</h2>
          <div class="badges">
            <%= partial "/assets/images/campaigns/you-cant-lose/150-free-power.min.svg" %>
            <%= partial "/assets/images/campaigns/you-cant-lose/guaranteed-savings.svg" %>
          </div>
          <p class="big">
            When you switch your main home to Powershop we’ll give you $150 free power, spread over your first six months. You’re also <a href="/guaranteed-savings">guaranteed to save</a> in your first year.
          </p>
          <hr/>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row plans padding white">
              <p class="big">Just pick the option that best suits you.</p>
              <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
                  <div class="white columns plan-container">
                      <h2 class="medium-text-center pink-type">Powershop Classic</h2>
                      <img style="
                              -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px 0px #fa0e6a;
                              -moz-box-shadow:    0px 0px 4px 0px #fa0e6a;
                              box-shadow:         0px 0px 4px 0px #fa0e6a;"
                              alt="Seasonal Plan" title="Go with the flow" src="/assets/images/resi/classic.png" />
                      <hr/>
                      <p>This option is for those who love a good bargain. It offers the <b>best overall value</b> through the extra savings you can make from buying our regular specials, and packs the full Powershop flavour.</p>
                      <ul style="text-align:left">
                        <li><b>Access to our online shop</b> where you can buy power as you go and save with regular specials.</li>
                        <li><b>Online tools and our mobile app</b> make it easy to track your usage.</li>
                        <li><b>Seasonal pricing</b> that reduces over spring and summer, then increases slightly over autumn and winter.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <%= partial "shared/sign_up_shopper" %>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns end">
                  <div class="white columns plan-container">
                      <h2 class="medium-text-center light-blue-type">Powershop Lite</h2>
                      <img alt="Fixed Plan" title="Fix and forget" src="/assets/images/resi/lite.png" />
                      <hr/>
                      <p>This is the option if you like a good deal but prefer a bit more simplicity, and don’t mind missing out on the extra savings you can get from shopping.</p>
                      <ul style="text-align:left">
                        <li>No access to the shop or our specials, just a simple monthly bill to pay.</li>
                        <li>Online tools and our handy mobile app make it easy to track your usage.</li>
                        <li>Fixed pricing that stays flat through the year.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <%= partial "shared/sign_up_light" %>
                  </div>
              </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="light-grey">
  <div class="row padding padding-bottom-last">
    <%= partial "shared/got_questions" %>
  </div>
</section>

<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function(){
    var cookie = readCookie("questionsOpen");
    if (cookie === "yes") {
      $('#got-questions').show();
    }
    // Define Vimeo player
    var iframe = $('#intro-video')[0];
    var player = $f(iframe);
    $('.vimeo .embed-container').click(function(event) {
      $(".embed-container").addClass("fade-background");
      $('.vimeo h3').fadeOut();
      $('.vimeo .play-btn').fadeOut();
      $('.vimeo .time').fadeOut();
      player.api('play');
    });
    $('#got-questions-link').click(function(){
      createCookie("questionsOpen", "yes", 1);
    })
  });
</script>
<script src="/assets/javascripts/third-party/froogaloop.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
